ugin manifest.yaml file\n35: - [ ] Create `integrations/dify-plugin/manifest.yaml`\n36: - [ ] Set `version: 0.0.2`\n37: - [ ] Set `type: plugin`\n38: - [ ] Set `author: volcano-sh`\n39: - [ ] Set `name: agentcube`\n40: - [ ] Add multilingual `label` entries (en_US, ja_JP, zh_Hans, pt_BR)\n41: - [ ] Add multilingual `description` entries\n42: - [ ] Set `icon: icon.png`\n43: - [ ] Set `icon_dark: icon-dark.png`\n44: - [ ] Configure `resource` section with `memory` and `permission` subtree\n45: - [ ] Add `plugins.tools: [provider/agentcube.yaml]`\n46: - [ ] Configure `meta` section with `version`, `arch` (amd64, arm64), and `runner`\n47: - [ ] Set `runner.language: python`, `runner.version: \"3.12\"`, `runner.entrypoint: main`\n48: - [ ] Set `minimum_dify_version: null`\n49: - [ ] Add `created_at`, `privacy`, `repo`, `verified` fields\n50: - [ ] Validate YAML syntax\n51: \n52: **Verification**:\n53: ```bash\n54: test -f integrations/dify-plugin/manifest.yaml && echo \"manifest.yaml exists\" || echo \"manifest.yaml missing\"\n55: yamllint integrations/dify-plugin/manifest.yaml || echo \"YAML syntax valid\"\n56: grep -q \"type: plugin\" integrations/dify-plugin/manifest.yaml && echo \"Plugin type configured\" || echo \"Plugin type missing\"\n57: grep -q \"plugins.tools\" integrations/dify-plugin/manifest.yaml && echo \"Tools configured\" || echo \"Tools missing\"\n58: ```\n59: \n60: **Acceptance Criteria**:\n61: - manifest.yaml follows exact Dify plugin structure\n62: - All required fields are present and correctly formatted\n63: - YAML syntax is valid\n64: - Multilingual labels are properly configured\n65: \n66: ---\n67: \n68: ### Task 3: Create provider descriptor YAML file\n69: - [ ] Create `integrations/dify-plugin/provider/agentcube.yaml`\n70: - [ ] Configure `identity.author: agentcube`\n71: - [ ] Configure `identity.name: agentcube`\n72: - [ ] Add multilingual `identity.label` entries\n73: - [ ] Add multilingual `identity.description` entries\n74: - [ ] Set `ident